            bindings = <
               &kp Q  &kp W  &kp E            &kp R  &kp T               &kp Y                &kp U       &kp I                  &kp O                &mt FSLH P
               &kp A  &kp S  &kp D            &kp F  &kp G               &kp H                &mt LPAR J  &mt RPAR K             &mt MINUS L          &mt SEMICOLON COLON
&mt LCTRL ESC  &kp Z  &kp X  &kp C            &kp V  &kp B               &kp N                &kp M       &mt EXCLAMATION COMMA  &mt QUESTION PERIOD  &mt SINGLE_QUOTE DOUBLE_QUOTES  &mt RIGHT_ALT RS(RC(BACKSPACE))
                             &mt LS(TAB) TAB  &mo 2  &mt LSHIFT SPACE    &mt LS(ENTER) ENTER  &mo 1       &kp BACKSPACE
            >;
